{"tid":588742,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本琵琶湖滑雪一問","createTime":"2018-03-11T12:07:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T17:20:18.000Z","uid":156996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fb6c0b87e4feb9b21b186c72c14f52bd6f845950","tid":588742,"uid":156996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T12:07:37.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我想問定d野先 <br />\n今年年尾去<br />\n<br />\n我同一班好兄弟今年年尾去日本學滑雪（5個人）<br />\n我本身都玩過下<br />\n但佢地4個未學過<br />\n我有上網睇過下d資料 但佢果邊好似冇咩英文教練<br />\n<br />\n我又想私人book<br />\n<br />\n集思廣益<br />\n其實點找私人滑雪教練（中 英文都ok）<br />\n點玩先抵玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac8cc63ae7f3c8d36abbc319756c6b60b44d4fa","tid":588742,"uid":133959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T13:36:35.000Z","msg":"5個人book團體堂咪得，定你想book 5個教練1對1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93fcdf8003374670d6d2d9f4bf0615b32a822b8b","tid":588742,"uid":172943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T18:37:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://Kkday.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FKkday.com&d=%2F4C5RZOQNvE4NBHarc2Aro9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=b509435a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Kkday.com</a>有得報當地一日遊，上次試過幾好，難波上車，走果時難波落返車"},{"pid":"a25b4a933c467495062bb4574a1abf7c586d8c2c","tid":588742,"uid":156996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93fcdf8003374670d6d2d9f4bf0615b32a822b8b","tid":588742,"uid":172943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T18:37:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://Kkday.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FKkday.com&d=%2F4C5RZOQNvE4NBHarc2Aro9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=b509435a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Kkday.c