me":"2018-03-12T17:14:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>琵琶湖同白馬個人認為都唔係for 初心者<br />\n近近赽<br />\n近近地湯沢gala 都唔錯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n白馬有11個場，一定會有適合初學者嘅雪道。<br />\n最緊要係容易搵中文教練。<br />\n<br />\n都係嗰句：請。教。練 !!"},{"pid":"39a45c285e53408825d445cab151c6a7d6739194","tid":588742,"uid":19613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T17:15:46.000Z","msg":"而家係越後滑緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a756e50f3bb18a196977e4f401e67263a8b65c9","tid":588742,"uid":16634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T17:20:18.000Z","msg":"滑兩個鐘就識啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}